{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|1Pe|5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","chapter":5,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v10","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":1,"text":"I exhort the elders among you as a fellow elder and witness to the sufferings of Christ, as well as one who shares in the glory about to be revealed:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":2,"text":"Shepherd God’s flock among you, not overseeing out of compulsion but willingly, as God would have you; not out of greed for money but eagerly;","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":3,"text":"not lording it over those entrusted to you, but being examples to the flock.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":4,"text":"And when the chief Shepherd appears, you will receive the unfading crown of glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":5,"text":"In the same way, you who are younger, be subject to the elders. All of you clothe yourselves with humility toward one another, because","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":6,"text":"Humble yourselves, therefore, under the mighty hand of God, so that he may exalt you at the proper time,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":7,"text":"casting all your cares on him, because he cares about you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":8,"text":"Be sober-minded, be alert. Your adversary the devil is prowling around like a roaring lion, looking for anyone he can devour.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":9,"text":"Resist him, firm in the faith, knowing that the same kind of sufferings are being experienced by your fellow believers throughout the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":10,"text":"The God of all grace, who called you to his eternal glory in Christ, will himself restore, establish, strengthen, and support you after you have suffered a little while.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":11,"text":"To him be dominion forever. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":12,"text":"Through Silvanus, a faithful brother (as I consider him), I have written to you briefly in order to encourage you and to testify that this is the true grace of God. Stand firm in it!","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":13,"text":"She who is in Babylon, chosen together with you, sends you greetings, as does Mark, my son.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","bookOrder":59,"chapter":5,"verse":14,"text":"Greet one another with a kiss of love. Peace to all of you who are in Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"1Pe","chapter":5,"paragraphStarts":[1,6,10,12],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"About the Elders"},{"beforeVerse":6,"text":"Conclusion"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I exhort the elders among you as a fellow elder and witness "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 4:20","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" to the sufferings of Christ, as well as one who shares in the glory about to be revealed: "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:18","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:4","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 4:20","book":"Act","chapter":4,"verse":20},{"label":"Rm 8:18","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":18},{"label":"Col 3:4","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:1Pe:5:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Shepherd God’s flock among you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:15","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:1","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 21:16","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:28","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":28,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" not overseeing "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss omit overseeing"},{"kind":"text","text":" out of compulsion but willingly, as God would have you; "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit as God would have you"},{"kind":"text","text":" not out of greed for money but eagerly; "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:15","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"vers